{"tid":106163,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"迷信撚召喚！ 有冇人求簽？（有圖）","createTime":"2017-02-03T12:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T08:46:39.000Z","uid":60319,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a43a482043f160f2945df78936cc996426716b2","tid":106163,"uid":60319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"想問有冇人信拜神果d e.g黃大仙 ，車公。<br />\n想問靈唔靈，因為小弟今日去車公求左支上簽，係問工作interview 順唔順利既，佢就話百事亨通同埋逢凶化吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/201952_d9ed8be1f55522ee8bee286d48f3fdb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F201952_d9ed8be1f55522ee8bee286d48f3fdb3.jpg&h=1df2a3af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇把打識解簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我搵左條友解佢好似亂咁黎就收左我廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n信：正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔信：負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c111ff25345ba2c2e9ccc75e95692d838a9d30","tid":106163,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:50:13.000Z","msg":"咁淺識字都識解嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52275dd32294ba14a3ce83f160636923fa12216c","tid":106163,"uid":60319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2374d2d91b2736d0193c6d0acd23674f2f42b7","tid":106163,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"求簽：why not"},{"pid":"2f3c95825186095ea1a014050485229998f204c8","tid":106163,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁淺識字都識解嘩<img src=\"/assets/f